# Don't copy these into the Docker image — keeps the image small and avoids
# stale node_modules from local Mac causing version drift on Railway.

server/node_modules/
**/node_modules/

# Local-only data + logs.
# These don't exist inside the build context (Portal/) anyway, but listed for
# clarity. The build context is Portal/ — Data/Operations/Config sit at the
# workspace root which Docker doesn't see.
# Note: NO unanchored `Config/` pattern here — that would also exclude
# server/config/ which contains plans.js. We hit that bug on 2026-05-27.

# Editor / OS junk
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/

# Tests / docs / nothing-the-server-needs
*.md
*.log
